'''Oston Rustam oʻgʻli Urunov''' (born 19 December 2000) is an Uzbek professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as an [[attacking midfielder]] for [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] club [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].<ref name="turkmenportal.com">{{Cite web |url=https://turkmenportal.com/blog/29223/futbolist-sbornoi-uzbekistana-oston-urunov-pereshel-v-spartak |title=Футболист сборной Узбекистана Остон Урунов перешел в "Спартак" |access-date=2020-08-20 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927155429/https://turkmenportal.com/blog/29223/futbolist-sbornoi-uzbekistana-oston-urunov-pereshel-v-spartak |url-status=live }}</ref>

==Club career==
Oston Urunov played in Uzbekistan for [[PFC Navbahor Namangan|Navbahor]] and [[PFC Lokomotiv Tashkent]]. In total, he played 55 matches in the [[Uzbekistan Super League]].<ref name="turkmenportal.com"/>

On 10 February 2020, Urunov signed a long-term contract with [[Russian Premier League]] club [[FC Ufa|Ufa]].<ref>{{cite press release|publisher=[[FC Ufa]]|url=http://www.fcufa.pro/component/k2/poluzashchitnik-sbornoj-uzbekistana-popolnil-sostav-fk-ufa|title=Полузащитник сборной Узбекистана пополнил состав ФК "Уфа"|date=10 February 2020|language=ru|access-date=10 February 2020|archive-date=12 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212085655/http://www.fcufa.pro/component/k2/poluzashchitnik-sbornoj-uzbekistana-popolnil-sostav-fk-ufa|url-status=live}}</ref> On 5 August 2020, [[FC Spartak Moscow|Spartak Moscow]] announced the signing of Urunov to a long-term contract from Ufa.<ref>{{cite web |title=Остон Урунов — новый игрок Спартака |url=https://spartak.com/news/2020-08-05-oston_urunov__novyy_igrok_spartaka/ |website=spartak.com/ |publisher=FC Spartak Moscow |access-date=5 August 2020 |language=ru |date=5 August 2020 |archive-date=6 August 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806204605/https://spartak.com/news/2020-08-05-oston_urunov__novyy_igrok_spartaka |url-status=live }}</ref> On 20 February 2021, he returned to [[FC Ufa|Ufa]] on loan with an option to purchase.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[FC Ufa]]|url=https://www.fcufa.pro/news-new/oston-urunov-dobro-pozhalovat-v-fk-ufa|title=Остон Урунов, добро пожаловать в ФК "Уфа"!|date=20 February 2021|language=ru|access-date=20 February 2021|archive-date=20 February 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220220430/https://www.fcufa.pro/news-new/oston-urunov-dobro-pozhalovat-v-fk-ufa|url-status=live}}</ref>

Upon his return from loan at Ufa, he was moved by Spartak to their second squad in the [[Russian Football National League]], [[FC Spartak-2 Moscow]].

On 19 August 2021, he returned to Ufa on another season-long loan, with an option to purchase.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[FC Ufa]]|url=https://www.fcufa.pro/news-new/oston-urunov-vozvrashchaetsya-v-fk-ufa|title=Остон Урунов возвращается в ФК "Уфа"!|date=19 August 2021|language=ru|access-date=19 August 2021|archive-date=19 August 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210819091009/https://www.fcufa.pro/news-new/oston-urunov-vozvrashchaetsya-v-fk-ufa|url-status=live}}</ref>

On 2 September 2022, Urunov's contract with Spartak was terminated by mutual consent.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Spartak Moscow|url=https://spartak.com/news/2022-09-02-spartak_rastorg_kontrakt_s_urunovym/|title="Спартак" расторг контракт с Уруновым|date=2 September 2022|access-date=2 September 2022|language=ru|archive-date=2 September 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220902100401/https://spartak.com/news/2022-09-02-spartak_rastorg_kontrakt_s_urunovym/|url-status=live}}</ref> On the same day, Urunov signed with [[FC Ural Yekaterinburg|Ural Yekaterinburg]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Ural Yekaterinburg|url=https://fc-ural.ru/novosti/glavnaya-komanda/uzbekskij-poluzashhitnik-oston-urunov-perehodit-v-ural|title=Узбекский полузащитник Остон Урунов переходит в "Урал"|date=2 September 2022|access-date=2 September 2022|language=ru|archive-date=2 September 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220902160250/https://fc-ural.ru/novosti/glavnaya-komanda/uzbekskij-poluzashhitnik-oston-urunov-perehodit-v-ural|url-status=live}}</ref> On 25 October 2022, Ural terminated the contract with Urunov by mutual consent.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Ural Yekaterinburg|url=https://fc-ural.ru/novosti/glavnaya-komanda/oston-urunov-pokidaet-ural|title=Остон Урунов покидает "Урал"|date=25 October 2022|language=ru|access-date=30 October 2022|archive-date=30 October 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20221030183933/https://fc-ural.ru/novosti/glavnaya-komanda/oston-urunov-pokidaet-ural|url-status=live}}</ref>

=== Persepolis ===
On 7 February 2024, Urunov joined [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] champions [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]] on a 18-month deal.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-02-07 |title=Persepolis hijack Esteghlal move for Oston Urunov |url=https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/494666/Persepolis-hijack-Esteghlal-move-for-Oston-Urunov |access-date=2024-02-08 |website=Tehran Times |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-02-08 |title=Persepolis Football Club signed contract with Oston Urunov |url=https://www.mojnews.com/Section-sports-7/536996-persepolis-football-club-signed-contract-with-oston-urunov |access-date=2024-02-08 |website=MojNews Agency |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=رنجکش |first=محسن |date=2024-02-07 |title="ارونوف" به پرسپولیس پیوست |url=https://fc-perspolis.com/14752-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%86%D9%88%D9%81-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%BE%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B3-%D9%BE%DB%8C%D9%88%D8%B3%D8%AA/ |access-date=2024-02-09 |website=باشگاه فرهنگی ورزشی پرسپولیس |language=fa-IR}}</ref>

He scored his first goal for Persepolis in a 4–2 victory over [[Foolad F.C.|Foolad]] on 8 March 2024.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-03-08 |title=ویدیو/ اولین گل اورونوف برای پرسپولیس روی همکاری دیدنی با ترابی |url=https://www.isna.ir/news/1402121812971/%D9%88%DB%8C%D8%AF%DB%8C%D9%88-%D8%A7%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%86-%DA%AF%D9%84-%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%86%D9%88%D9%81-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%BE%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B3-%D8%B1%D9%88%DB%8C-%D9%87%D9%85%DA%A9%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D8%AF%DB%8C%D8%AF%D9%86%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%A7-%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%A8%DB%8C |access-date=2024-03-18 |website=ایسنا |language=fa}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=اولین گل از راه رسید: اورونوف مثل یک ستاره |url=https://www.varzesh3.com/news/2007530/%D8%A7%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%86-%DA%AF%D9%84-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%87-%D8%B1%D8%B3%DB%8C%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%86%D9%88%D9%81-%D9%85%D8%AB%D9%84-%DB%8C%DA%A9-%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%87 |access-date=2024-03-18 |website=ورزش سه |language=fa}}</ref>

==International career==
Urunov made his international debut for [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan]] in a friendly 2–0 defeat to [[Turkey national football team|Turkey]] on 2 June 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2019/06/02/world/friendlies/t-rkiye/uzbekistan/3018557/|title=Türkiye vs Uzbekistan - 2 June 2019 - Soccerway|website=int.soccerway.com}}</ref>

He scored his first international goal on 11 June 2022 against [[Maldives national football team|Maldives]] at the [[Markaziy Stadium (Namangan)|Namangan Markaziy Stadium]] during the [[2023 AFC Asian Cup qualification – third round|2023 AFC Asian Cup qualification]].<ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=https://www.gazeta.uz/ru/2022/06/12/uzb-maldives/|title=Отбор Кубка Азии-2023: Узбекистан разгромил Мальдивы|website=Gazeta.uz|language=Russian|date=12 June 2022|access-date=2 August 2023|archive-date=3 August 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230803024106/https://www.gazeta.uz/ru/2022/06/12/uzb-maldives/|url-status=live}}</ref>

